# hash-newline-mid-file

## Input

```
#
k v

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..6
  COMMENT@0..1
    SHARP@0..1 "#"
  NEWLINE@1..2 "\n"
  ENTRY@2..6
    WORD_KEY@2..3
      WORD@2..3 "k"
    SPACE@3..4 " "
    LINE_STRING@4..5
      STRING@4..5 "v"
    NEWLINE@5..6 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@2..3 "k",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@4..5 "v",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

